{"TopicId":186511,"ForumId":39,"TopicTitle":"Behold the KSP-HOTASABBAK Controller (Kerbal Space Program - Hands on Throttle and Stick and Button Box and Keyboard), just in time for the 50th anniversary of the Apollo 11 moon landing.","CreatedByName":"MelkorsGreatestHits","CreatedById":198894,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-19T18:13:07Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"MelkorsGreatestHits","CreatedById":198894,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-19T18:13:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022xcFIQt7_d.jpg?maxwidth=640\u0026amp;shape=thumb\u0026amp;f\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002275.00\u0022 height=\u0022480\u0022 width=\u0022640\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/xcFIQt7_d.jpg?maxwidth=640\u0026amp;shape=thumb\u0026amp;fidelity=medium\u0022\u003EBehold the KSP-HOTASABBAK Controller (Kerbal Space Program - Hands on Throttle and Stick and Button Box and Keyboard), just in time for the 50th anniversary of the Apollo 11 moon landing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFull Imgur album link:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://imgur.com/a/8uzr5yu\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://imgur.com/a/8uzr5yu\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAfter a project about a month ago, I ended up with an extra USB controller board sitting around unused and that wouldn\u0027t do. So I decided to make another thing.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis USB controller is inspired by Apollo and early Space Shuttle-era NASA. It\u0027s housed in a TI-99/4A case and retains the mechanical keyboard from that unit.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt has:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0026gt;4 axes\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0026gt;22 gamepad/joystick buttons\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0026gt;lights\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0026gt;beeping alarms\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0026gt;a functional keyboard (also via the USB)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClick the link above for a tour, build walk through, and a couple of videos of it in action.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-07-19T21:29:19Z\u0022 title=\u002207/19/2019 09:29  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 19, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by MelkorsGreatestHits\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EBad link\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-19T19:07:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nConsidering my favorite game on the TI-99 was Parsec, another space game, this is a fitting makeover.\u00A0\u00A0 Does the voice synthesizer still work?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mahnarch","CreatedById":114432,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-19T19:27:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou know that gif where Chris Pratt is playing the office guy on TV and he smiles big and looks at the camera?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nImagine I posted that, since I got in trouble last time I just posted a reaction gif with no words on it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CobaltWolf","CreatedById":105588,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-19T20:12:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhoa\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-19T20:13:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNoice!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nYour imgur embedded link is messed up... \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gunnerline","CreatedById":198860,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-19T20:14:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is superbly done!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbart","CreatedById":78303,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-19T20:53:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA Kerbal-worthy monstrosit, and wow, a TI-99...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy one suggestion would be to rename it\u00A0\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003EKSP-HO\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003ET\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003EA\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003ESA\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003EBBA\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003EKFTSABRSAWWMMANM C\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003Eontroller (Kerbal\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u00A0Space Program - Hands\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003Eon T\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003Ehrottle and St\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003Eick and Button Box and Keyboard)\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\uFEFF for Flying Through Space, Air and Beyond and Rovering the Surface As Well, With Many More Applications Not Mentioned,\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003EBecause, if you\u2019re going for a gluttonous abbreviation, why not go all the way?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MelkorsGreatestHits","CreatedById":198894,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-19T21:30:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223637603\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186511\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221563567214\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002277721\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stone Blue\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Stone Blue said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNoice!\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nYour imgur embedded link is messed up... \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFixed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cavscout74","CreatedById":181783,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-19T21:51:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223637527\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186511\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221563559987\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022198894\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MelkorsGreatestHits\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, MelkorsGreatestHits said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s housed in a TI-99/4A case\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow, I haven\u0027t heard that mentioned in ages, that was my first computer.\u00A0 Wonderful job on the controller!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223637557\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186511\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221563563220\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCo\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Ensidering my favorite game on \u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Ethe TI-99 was Pa\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Erse\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Ec\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat was one of my favorites too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"magnemoe","CreatedById":57801,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-20T11:56:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGenial and very nice with the right side area who I assume was for cartridges.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nImpressive getting the keyboard to work to, I assume you mapped the function keys to the numbers\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Maxsimal","CreatedById":160254,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-22T16:19:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVery impressive!\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Frank_G","CreatedById":100000,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-22T17:11:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan a controller be more kerbal? Very cool \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AHHans","CreatedById":197939,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-22T18:36:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t think it has enough buttons!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSCNR. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-22T18:40:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Retro Computers enthusiast inside me is screaming desperately \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E(And yeah - I have a working TI99 myself - with speech and a MiniPEB!)\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003Ethe KSP enthusiast is trying to shout \u0022Kudos\u0022 over the screaming. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue2.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"defcon.klaxon","CreatedById":19994,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-22T19:23:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a fantastic build, excellent work \u003Cabbr title=\